7#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/RewriteOutArgs.h"
8#include "compiler/translator/tree_util/IntermRebuild.h"

10using namespace sh;
11
12namespace
13{
14
15template <typename T>
16class SmallMultiSet
17{
18 public:
19 struct Entry
20 {
21 T elem;
22 size_t count;
23 };
24
25 const Entry *find(const T &x) const
26 {
27 for (auto &entry : mEntries)
28 {
29 if (x == entry.elem)
30 {
31 return &entry;
32 }
33 }
34 return nullptr;
35 }
36
37 size_t multiplicity(const T &x) const
38 {
39 const Entry *entry = find(x);
40 return entry ? entry->count : 0;
41 }
42
43 const Entry &insert(const T &x)
44 {
45 Entry *entry = findMutable(x);
46 if (entry)
47 {
48 ++entry->count;
49 return *entry;
50 }
51 else
52 {
53 mEntries.push_back({x, 1});
54 return mEntries.back();
55 }
56 }
57
58 void clear() { mEntries.clear(); }
59
60 bool empty() const { return mEntries.empty(); }
61
62 size_t uniqueSize() const { return mEntries.size(); }
63
64 private:
65 ANGLE_INLINE Entry *findMutable(const T &x) { return const_cast<Entry *>(find(x)); }
66
67 private:
68 std::vector<Entry> mEntries;
69};
70
71const TVariable *GetVariable(TIntermNode &node)
72{
73 TIntermTyped *tyNode = node.getAsTyped();
74 ASSERT(tyNode);
75 if (TIntermSymbol *symbol = tyNode->getAsSymbolNode())
76 {
77 return &symbol->variable();
78 }
79 return nullptr;
80}
81
82class Rewriter : public TIntermRebuild
83{
84 SmallMultiSet<const TVariable *> mVarBuffer; // reusable buffer
85 SymbolEnv &mSymbolEnv;
86
87 public:
88 ~Rewriter() override { ASSERT(mVarBuffer.empty()); }
89
90 Rewriter(TCompiler &compiler, SymbolEnv &symbolEnv)
91 : TIntermRebuild(compiler, false, true), mSymbolEnv(symbolEnv)
92 {}
93
94 static bool argAlreadyProcessed(TIntermTyped *arg)
95 {
96 if (arg->getAsAggregate())
97 {
98 const TFunction *func = arg->getAsAggregate()->getFunction();
99 if (func && func->symbolType() == SymbolType::AngleInternal && func->name() == "swizzle_ref")
100 {
101 return true;
102 }
103 }
104 return false;
105 }
106
107 PostResult visitAggregatePost(TIntermAggregate &aggregateNode) override
108 {
109 ASSERT(mVarBuffer.empty());
110
111 const TFunction *func = aggregateNode.getFunction();
112 if (!func)
113 {
114 return aggregateNode;
115 }
116
117 TIntermSequence &args = *aggregateNode.getSequence();
118 size_t argCount = args.size();
119
120 auto getParamQualifier = [&](size_t i) {
121 const TVariable &param = *func->getParam(i);
122 const TType &paramType = param.getType();
123 const TQualifier paramQual = paramType.getQualifier();
124 switch (paramQual)
125 {
126 case TQualifier::EvqOut:
127 case TQualifier::EvqInOut:
128 if (!mSymbolEnv.isReference(param))
129 {
130 mSymbolEnv.markAsReference(param, AddressSpace::Thread);
131 }
132 break;
133 default:
134 break;
135 }
136 return paramQual;
137 };
138
139 bool mightAlias = false;
140
141 for (size_t i = 0; i < argCount; ++i)
142 {
143 const TQualifier paramQual = getParamQualifier(i);
144
145 switch (paramQual)
146 {
147 case TQualifier::EvqOut:
148 case TQualifier::EvqInOut:
149 {
150 const TVariable *var = GetVariable(*args[i]);
151 if (mVarBuffer.insert(var).count > 1)
152 {
153 mightAlias = true;
154 i = argCount;
155 }
156 }
157 break;
158
159 default:
160 break;
161 }
162 }
163
164 const bool hasIndeterminateVar = mVarBuffer.find(nullptr);
165
166 if (!mightAlias)
167 {
168 mightAlias = hasIndeterminateVar && mVarBuffer.uniqueSize() > 1;
169 }
170
171 if (mightAlias)
172 {
173 for (size_t i = 0; i < argCount; ++i)
174 {
175 TIntermTyped *arg = args[i]->getAsTyped();
176 ASSERT(arg);
177 if (!argAlreadyProcessed(arg))
178 {
179 const TVariable *var = GetVariable(*arg);
180 const TQualifier paramQual = getParamQualifier(i);
181
182 if (hasIndeterminateVar || mVarBuffer.multiplicity(var) > 1)
183 {
184 switch (paramQual)
185 {
186 case TQualifier::EvqOut:
187 args[i] = &mSymbolEnv.callFunctionOverload(Name("out"), arg->getType(),
188 *new TIntermSequence{arg});
189 break;
190
191 case TQualifier::EvqInOut:
192 args[i] = &mSymbolEnv.callFunctionOverload(
193 Name("inout"), arg->getType(), *new TIntermSequence{arg});
194 break;
195
196 default:
197 break;
198 }
199 }
200 }
201 }
202 }
203
204 mVarBuffer.clear();
205
206 return aggregateNode;
207 }
208};
209
210} // anonymous namespace
211
212bool sh::RewriteOutArgs(TCompiler &compiler, TIntermBlock &root, SymbolEnv &symbolEnv)
213{
214 Rewriter rewriter(compiler, symbolEnv);
215 if (!rewriter.rebuildRoot(root))
216 {
217 return false;
218 }
219 return true;
220}
